OL,7,FKen Reid was loved by journalists and
OL,8,Frespected by politicians from across
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland and beyond, mourners
OL,10,Fat his funeral have been told.
OL,12,FHundreds of people packed into St
OL,13,FPatrick's Church in Ballymena, Co
OL,14,FAntrim, for a service of thanksgiving
OL,15,Ffor the former UTV political editor
OL,16,Fwho died last week at the age of 69
OL,17,Fafter an illness.
OL,19,FKen was known for reporting on many of
OL,20,Fthe worst atrocities of the Troubles
OL,21,Fbefore chronicling the peace process.
