OL,7,FPoliticians past and present were
OL,8,Frepresented at the service. Stormont
OL,9,Fspeaker Edwin Poots and Ulster
OL,10,FUnionist Party leader Mike Nesbitt, a
OL,11,Fformer colleague of Mr Reid at UTV,
OL,12,Fwere among those who attended.
OL,14,FFormer MP Lady Sylvia Hermon and ex-
OL,15,FAlliance Party leader David Ford were
OL,16,Falso in the church.
