OL,7,FDozens of journalists who had worked
OL,8,Fwith Mr Reid over several decades also
OL,9,Fattended the funeral. Former UTV
OL,10,Fjournalists Ivan Little, Frank
OL,11,FMitchell and Fearghal McKinney were
OL,12,Fjoined by current political editor
OL,13,FTracey Magee and presenters Paul Clark
OL,14,Fand Rose Neill.
OL,16,FBBC journalist Mark Simpson delivered
OL,17,Fthe eulogy, stating that everyone who
OL,18,Fhad worked with Mr Reid would treasure
OL,19,Fthe time they had spent with him.
