OL,7,FHe told the mourners: "It is not often
OL,8,Fyou hear Stormont and love in the same
OL,9,Fsentence, but the Stormont press pack
OL,10,Floved Ken Reid.
OL,12,F"It was a cross-community love, UTV
OL,13,Fand BBC. He was also loved by RTE,
OL,14,FSky, Downtown, Irish Times, the Press
OL,15,FAssociation, you name it, newspaper
OL,16,Fjournalists, even the press officers
OL,17,Fat Stormont loved Ken Reid.
