OL,7,FAddressing the family in the church,
OL,8,Fhe said: "You were his pride and joy.
OL,9,FHe had so much pride in all of you."
OL,11,FHe added: "During 27 years at UTV Ken
OL,12,Fhad to explain the complicated,
OL,13,Ftangled, complex world of Stormont
OL,14,Fpolitics on live television in front
OL,15,Fof a huge audience and he made it look
OL,16,Feasy. He really did.
OL,18,F"At UTV he didn't report the news, he
OL,19,Fwas the news. ITV may have had their
OL,20,FNews at 10, but we had our News at
OL,21,FKen."
