OL,7,FMr Simpson said when Ken Reid joined
OL,8,FUTV in 1994, Albert Reynolds was
OL,9,Ftaoiseach, Bill Clinton was in the
OL,10,FWhite House and the UK prime minister
OL,11,Fwas John Major.
OL,13,FHe added: "Ken being Ken, it wasn't
OL,14,Flong before he had interviewed every
OL,15,Fone of them.
OL,17,F"And so it went on. Ken interviewed
OL,18,Fall the key players in London, Dublin,
OL,19,FWashington and Belfast for almost
OL,20,Fthree decades. Seven prime ministers
OL,21,Fin total."
