OL,7,FMr Simpson said that although
OL,8,Fjournalists were always in
OL,9,Fcompetition, Mr Reid had taken the
OL,10,Ftime "to build deep friendships at
OL,11,FStormont".
OL,13,FMr Reid is survived by his wife Liz
OL,14,Fand children Gareth, Sarah and Sophie.
OL,15,FHe will be cremated later following a
OL,16,Fprivate family service.
